<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>55</hymn_number>
<author>Taivela</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nei hehpih zieka maw Lalpa na thawkna,
 Hun en zui ka, Kalvari tang tiengin;
 Linglukhuk khu kawma Na mel thisan luong chu,
 Ka hun en ngam puoi ana bek ie Lalpa!

[V2]
 Nei hehpihna cheng cheng,
 Thu'n vang ka gen seng puoi;
 Na min ka pak ding bang hin,
 Lalpa, aw ka hun pak thei puoi.

[V3]
 2. Mipi a enhaw chu laina a um puou,
 &quot;Ka dang a chak&quot; tia, A kiko khan;
 Ka Lalpa dang chak tulh ding kuomah cha umlo,
 A nget loh hiel zuthuk leh thil kha a pieu.

[V4]
 3. Na khuk bang hi Lalpa, kuo-a a khu um?
 A kilawm puoi, Nang dingin linglukhuk;
 Na van Lal kraun lul chu khawi taka um a him?
 Muhsitna puonsan leh ling phek chu Na khuk?

[V5]
 4. A thawklai mel en chun ngilh ding guol ei puoi,
 Lei leh van Lal nang leh kei ziekin maw;
 Lungkhamna thuok kha lo lungkham in A mau a,
 Chawian hitiu hehpihna Lal deihum chu.</lyrics>
<title>Hehpih Ziek In</title>
</song>